<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">三十年软件先锋，二十载职教示范</span></p><p style="text-align: left;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">创业创新，知识管理</span></p><p style="text-align: left;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">学好软件，报效祖国</span></p><p style="text-align: left;"><span style="color: rgb(131, 45, 143);"><strong>江西软件大学20周年华诞</strong></span></p><p style="text-align: left;"><span style="color: rgb(131, 45, 143);"><strong>先锋软件集团30周年庆典</strong></span></p><p style="text-align: left;"><span style="color: rgb(131, 45, 143);"><strong>“双庆”同喜，恭贺芳华</strong></span></p><p style="text-align: left;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">让我们一同走进当天的五个论坛现场</span></p><p style="text-align: left;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">感受那些精彩时刻</span></p><p style="text-align: left;">2024中国软件井冈山先锋主论坛</p><p style="text-align: left;"><strong>群英荟萃，齐聚井冈</strong></p><p style="text-align: left;"><span style="color: rgb(131, 45, 143);"><strong>经验分享，对话未来</strong></span></p><p style="text-align: left;">《支持大模型训练和推理的自主可控的基础设施》</p><p style="text-align: left;">《区块链与区块链服务网络(BSN)》等</p><p style="text-align: left;">主题报告吸引了广大参会者</p><p style="text-align: left;">报告内容丰富、思想深刻、鞭辟入里</p><p style="text-align: left;">为广大校友师生带来了一场精彩绝伦的学术盛宴</p><p style="text-align: left;">加深了校友与师生之间的情感联系和学术合作</p><p style="text-align: left;"><br></p><p style="text-align: left;"><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746685557702.png" alt="1746685557702.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746685557702.png" style="width: 100%;"></p><p style="text-align: left;"><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746685537223.png" alt="1746685537223.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746685537223.png" style="width: 100%;"></p><p style="text-align: left;"><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746685517943.png" alt="1746685517943.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746685517943.png" style="width: 100%;"></p><p style="text-align: left;">新时代人才培养与经济社会发展论坛</p><p style="text-align: left;"><br></p><p style="text-align: left;"><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746685457302.png" alt="1746685457302.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746685457302.png" style="width: 100%;"><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746685432423.png" alt="1746685432423.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746685432423.png" style="width: 100%;"></p><p style="text-align: left;"><br></p><p style="text-align: left;"><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746685413966.png" alt="1746685413966.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746685413966.png" style="width: 100%;"><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746685407541.png" alt="1746685407541.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746685407541.png" style="width: 100%;"></p><p style="text-align: left;"><br></p><p style="text-align: left;"><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746685398606.png" alt="1746685398606.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746685398606.png" style="width: 100%;"></p><p style="text-align: left;"><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746685392947.png" alt="1746685392947.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746685392947.png" style="width: 100%;"></p><p style="text-align: left;"><br></p><p style="text-align: left;">新时代信创产业发展趋势论坛</p><p style="text-align: left;"><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746685376546.png" alt="1746685376546.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746685376546.png" style=""><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746685368981.png" alt="1746685368981.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746685368981.png" style="width: 100%;"></p><p style="text-align: left;"><br></p><p style="text-align: left;"><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746685362261.png" alt="1746685362261.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746685362261.png" style="width: 100%;"></p><p style="text-align: left;"><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746685349921.png" alt="1746685349921.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746685349921.png" style="width: 100%;"><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746685333782.png" alt="1746685333782.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746685333782.png" style="width: 100%;"></p><p style="text-align: left;"><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746685322257.png" alt="1746685322257.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746685322257.png" style="width: 100%;"></p><p style="text-align: left;"><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746685308747.png" alt="1746685308747.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746685308747.png" style="width: 100%;"><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746685295761.png" alt="1746685295761.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746685295761.png" style="width: 100%;"></p><p style="text-align: left;"><br></p><p style="text-align: left;"><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746685287963.png" alt="1746685287963.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746685287963.png" style="width: 100%;"></p><p style="text-align: left;">区块链技术与人才培养新模式论坛</p><p style="text-align: left;"><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746685233221.png" alt="1746685233221.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746685233221.png" style="width: 100%;"><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746685212022.png" alt="1746685212022.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746685212022.png" style="width: 100%;"></p><p style="text-align: left;"><br></p><p style="text-align: left;"><strong>AHEAD-先锋</strong></p><p style="text-align: left;"><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746685196224.png" alt="1746685196224.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746685196224.png" style="width: 100%;"></p><p style="text-align: left;"><br></p><p style="text-align: left;"><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746685184981.png" alt="1746685184981.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746685184981.png" style="width: 100%;"></p><p style="text-align: left;"><br></p><p style="text-align: left;">井冈山江西软件大学校友论坛</p><p style="text-align: left;"><br></p><p style="text-align: left;"><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746685164862.png" alt="1746685164862.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746685164862.png" style="width: 100%;"></p><p style="text-align: left;"><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746685154502.png" alt="1746685154502.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746685154502.png" style="width: 100%;"></p><p style="text-align: left;"><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746685144002.png" alt="1746685144002.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746685144002.png" style="width: 100%;"></p><p style="text-align: left;"><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746685128581.png" alt="1746685128581.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746685128581.png" style="width: 100%;"></p><p style="text-align: left;"><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746685112342.png" alt="1746685112342.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746685112342.png" style="width: 100%;"></p><p style="text-align: left;"><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746685095622.png" alt="1746685095622.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746685095622.png" style="width: 100%;"></p><p style="text-align: left;"><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746685083942.png" alt="1746685083942.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746685083942.png" style="width: 100%;"></p><p style="text-align: left;"><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746685066502.png" alt="1746685066502.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746685066502.png" style="width: 100%;"></p><p style="text-align: left;"><br></p><p style="text-align: left;"><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746685059262.png" alt="1746685059262.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746685059262.png" style="width: 100%;"></p><p style="text-align: left;"><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746685050501.png" alt="1746685050501.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746685050501.png" style="width: 100%;"></p><p style="text-align: left;"><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746685041142.png" alt="1746685041142.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746685041142.png" style="width: 100%;"></p><p style="text-align: left;"><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746685031061.png" alt="1746685031061.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746685031061.png" style="width: 100%;"></p><p style="text-align: left;"><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746685018183.png" alt="1746685018183.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746685018183.png" style="width: 100%;"></p><p style="text-align: left;"><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746684998422.png" alt="1746684998422.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746684998422.png" style="width: 100%;"></p><p style="text-align: left;"><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746684988802.png" alt="1746684988802.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746684988802.png" style="width: 100%;"></p><p style="text-align: left;"><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746684982017.png" alt="1746684982017.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746684982017.png" style="width: 100%;"></p><p style="text-align: left;"><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746684971143.png" alt="1746684971143.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746684971143.png" style="width: 100%;"></p><p style="text-align: left;"><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746684954002.png" alt="1746684954002.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746684954002.png" style="width: 100%;"></p><p style="text-align: left;"><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746684941336.png" alt="1746684941336.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746684941336.png" style="width: 100%;"><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746684943181.png" alt="1746684943181.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746684943181.png" style=""></p><p style="text-align: left;"><br></p><p style="text-align: left;"><span style="color: rgb(131, 45, 143);"><strong>三十载软件先锋，勇拓国产软件之路</strong></span></p><p style="text-align: left;"><span style="color: rgb(131, 45, 143);"><strong>二十载职教典范，雕琢时代工匠之才</strong></span></p><p style="text-align: left;">学校将始终坚守井冈山精神</p><p style="text-align: left;">聚力人才培育，秉持创新引领</p><p style="text-align: left;">强化科技攻关，促进产业转型</p><p style="text-align: left;">竭力培育更多德才兼备</p><p style="text-align: left;">技艺精湛的高端技术技能人才</p>